{
  "stem": "22734.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they called me Evicka.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Anyhow, so that was that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we had enough to eat in Terezin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Basically, I mean, we were not overfed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we were not starving.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we managed to feed the parents.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We had potatoes and things and cucumbers and tomatoes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we bartered.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And-- and we were scared that they would send us east.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then in September of 1942, '43-- I mean, we were there a year.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So what did we do there?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- we worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we tried to be alone as much as we could, which was difficult because Terezin was crowded.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Here and there, we went to a concert.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were always in the attic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Or there was a performance of one or two operas.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They did mostly They did the opera that was produced for-- the children's opera for Theresienstadt, which was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, they had the poetry reading always in the attic.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the music was-- if there was a concert, it was wonderful because the musicians were from all over Europe.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were all first class musicians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that-- that was really uplifting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the operas were also uplifting.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I think they had-- did once or attempted to do something of that sort.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Anyway, that was the life in Terezin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "You-- you hustled for your daily bread.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And you try to steal a few minutes alone.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- and you tried to stay healthy if that was in your power, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And then came September 1943.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And there was a transport going east, big one, 5,000.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "There was nothing for about six months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So it was a big lull and then all of a sudden, 5,000 people.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we were all in it.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
